reviewText: Super helpful tips and tricks for someone that is very basic with makeup. Great video for a beginner! Shes also a award winning makeup artist in Las Vegas specializing in weddings. [...]

Brianna's makeup techniques helped me to easily improve my look 110%! I am 49 years old and wish I had met Brianna Thompson when I was 25!  Her video was easy to follow and more importantly, easy to implement the techniques in real life. Her charismatic personality makes it really fun to learn and to put on makeup again. My eyes really pop now and my nose is more narrow thanks to an easy trick she teaches!  I also look 10 years younger!  Better than any department store makeover I have ever had!  Thanks Brianna!!!
